      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 38, United States Code, to provide a presumption of service connection for injuries classified as cold weather injuries which occur in veterans who while engaged in military operations had sustained exposure to cold weather.</title>
